Grab a big bowl and toss in 500g of bread flour (or all-purpose, dont overthink it) with 350g of lukewarm water. Stir it into a shaggy mess. Youre not kneading, just mixing. Cover the bowl and walk away for 3045 minutes. Let the flour and water get to know each other, this is the autolyse, where the magic begins.</p><p class="text-black-800 font-ui py-2 text-[15px] leading-[150%] tracking-[-1.65%] hidden 2xl:block">Come back. Cover the bowl and walk away for 3045 minutes. Let the flour and water get to know each other, this is the autolyse, where the magic begins.</p><p class="text-black-800 font-ui py-2 text-[15px] leading-[150%] tracking-[-1.65%] hidden 2xl:block">Come back.
